%B0-Ng%C3%B4-H%C6%B0ng/poem-hgnlEy3g1ZrQeSQ_qIlN0g">Ngụ cư Ngô Hưng - 寓居吳興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-K%E1%BB%B7/author-rrGRphgHzx_THgdF6hbcZQ">Tăng Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Thu-nhi%E1%BB%87t/poem-azJCHzp5440CKfyUA9-Bmw">Thu nhiệt - 秋熱</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba/poem-yyvN0UBUnP8iJxadLpZdoQ">Tị địa - 避地</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD/poem-4_3r_tUgn4sXO_w33S1XKA">Tống Cao tam thập ngũ thư ký - 送高三十五書記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
